        # (sha 70da390c42f4, 101,733 bytes -- not the generated brand
        # fallback), so the remaining suspects are OUTSIDE the window:
        # an AUMID registry key or a stale pin/shortcut. Now: the
        # diagnosis runs on the native path right after the line his log
        # reaches, again at 30s; apply_app_icon reads the icon BACK
